  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UN Global Compact Africa Strategy 2022-2024</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The development objective of the project is &#x201C;to mainstream corporate sustainability practices across Africa, resulting in African businesses making meaningful contributions to the SDGs&#x201D;. This will be achieved through two outcomes: 1) A significant numbers of African companies of all sizes have become UN Global Compact members and are committed to the Ten Principles and 2) African companies of all sizes are enabled to integrate the Ten Principles and SDGs into their core strategy and operations.</narrative>
  </description>
